This directory contains alternative interpolation routines
for use in the PARAMESH package.








Linear interpolation with a Muscl type monotonization constraint.
-----------------------------------------------------------------

Use files
            muscl_amr_1blk_cc_prol_gen_unk_fun.f
            muscl_amr_1blk_cc_prol_gen_work_fun.f
            muscl_amr_1blk_fc_prol_gen_fun.f
in place of the followong files in the default distribution
            amr_1blk_cc_prol_gen_unk_fun.f
            amr_1blk_cc_prol_gen_work_fun.f
            amr_1blk_fc_prol_gen_fun.f

